DOKO BUNNE SONG LYRICS :- 

Hookline :- 
Doko Bunne Nigalo Choyale
Jyanai Khayo Tyo Timro Moyale

Bhetinai Chhode Hajur Bar Pipal Chhaya
Uhile ta Lekhinthyo re Chithimaa Maya

Nachna Gauna Rodhimai Gayinthyo ni hai
Sathi sangi sabai chhute kaha gaya khoi
Sailiko tyo bolima adkinthyo man
Samjhana bhai bilai gaya ramaila ti chhen

Chhoto Jiwan Sang Sangai Hasaula
Nalau Pirim chhodera Janebhaa

Pahile Pahile ta Maya Lambhanda Gharkale dinthena re
Ahile ahile ta jali chhan sabai chokai mayai bhetinna re

Samjhana Sati Mayako Chino Kusume Rumal
Lairakhe Saili Nabirsiyos Maya Yo Jyanlai Sochera

#dokobunne #keharlimbu #kumarimovie #akritirajbhandari #abishekkhadka #dokobunnenigalochoyale #keharlimbunewsong #newmoviesong #nepalimovie

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Lyrics: 
Lu hai Manungkotaima mero dil basyo lali othaimaa.
Lu hai manung kotaima najar nalagau lali othaima.

Pirati lam na ta Saili ghumna lai jamna ta.
Pirati launna ma Saila ekdine pauna sa.

Oi hoi damauli katesi madiko pool hitaiko mayalai gulab ko phool.

Ghara mero rukumai timi Mam pareu ukhumai.
Ghar mero tanahu ho launa ke bhanam bhanam bho.

Na rup maa khot timro sundar gulabi otha timro.
Ke hereu tesari o kho laaj lagyo besari.

O hoi marsyandi salala paniko bhel kisimai raichha ni mayako khel.

Tan ramro Mam ramro timi lajauda jhan ramro.
Jiu pani kasilo timro muharai hasilo.

Ke socheu bhanata timle paraichheu Manata.
Ma ta gurung ki chhori ho mero khyalmai dil chori bho.

snippet.title: VEK X Oshin Karki - Pari Katha (Prod. by SNJV ) (ClassX Rush Live Track 2)
snippet.description:
ClassX Rush - Live Track No. 2 

From hearing her voice on an Instagram Live to finally creating together this truly feels like a dream come true.

In this episode of ClassX RUSH - LIVE, watch and listen as Oshin and I craft a complete track from scratch in just 3 hours and 13 minutes. From the first idea to writing every word, shaping melodies, and building the final sound.

This session captures the beauty of spontaneous creativity, collaboration, and trusting the process.
I want to extend a huge thank you to our extremely talented producers, SNJV and POZOD, who played a major role in creating this masterpiece.
Much love as well to my brothers KEEMA , NIXDII and SAGE for the incredible company and energy throughout the session. ü§ç

ClassX RUSH - LIVE is a space where ideas turn into music and artists come together to create without boundaries. This is only the beginning many more exciting artists will be joining this journey very soon.

Performed by:

snippet.title: ‡§Ö‡§≤‡•ç‡§≤‡§æ‡§∞‡•á ‡§®‡§æ‡§®‡•Ä ‡§ï‡•á‡§∏‡•Ä "Allare Nani Kesi" Yubaraj Portel(Cover Remake) | Old is Gold | Music Nepal
snippet.description:
Experience a fresh take on the timeless Nepali folk classic, "Allare Nani Kesi." Originally composed and sung by the legendary Jhalakman Gandharva, this remake version is beautifully reimagined by Yubaraj Portel only on Music Nepal's Official YouTube Channel.

This version brings modern production while keeping the soulful essence of the Sarangi and the traditional Gandharva roots alive for a new generation.

"‡§Ö‡§≤‡•ç‡§≤‡§æ‡§∞‡•á ‡§®‡§æ‡§®‡•Ä" (Allare Nani Kesi) ‡§è‡§â‡§ü‡§æ ‡§ï‡§æ‡§≤‡§ú‡§Ø‡•Ä ‡§®‡•á‡§™‡§æ‡§≤‡•Ä ‡§≤‡•ã‡§ï ‡§ó‡•Ä‡§§ ‡§π‡•ã‡•§  ‡§Ø‡•Å‡§µ‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú ‡§™‡•ã‡§∞‡•ç‡§ü‡•á‡§≤‡§ï‡•ã ‡§∞‡§ø‡§Æ‡•á‡§ï ‡§∏‡§Ç‡§∏‡•ç‡§ï‡§∞‡§£ ‡§∞ ‡§ù‡§≤‡§ï‡§Æ‡§æ‡§® ‡§ó‡§®‡•ç‡§ß‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§Æ‡•å‡§≤‡§ø‡§ï (Original) ‡§∏‡§Ç‡§∏‡•ç‡§ï‡§∞‡§£‡§Æ‡§æ,

This folk melody reflects the culture, tradition, and heartfelt emotions of Nepali villages. A perfect combination of soulful lyrics, traditional instruments, and rhythmic beats.
Enjoy the real taste of Nepali Lok Geet Dohori and regional music heritage. Celebrate the spirit of Nepal through Music Nepal‚Äôs timeless Lok Geet collection, bringing together authentic Nepali folk sounds. Experience soulful traditional music with rich melodies and heartfelt folk emotions.  A beautiful blend of lok dohori and classic traditional rhythms that portray love, devotion, culture, and village life.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

snippet.title: Rze- Gimme The Loot x Manas Ghale(PROD BY SHIGU)
snippet.description:
BLACKHOUSEMOB presents Gimme The Loot From The album RZE (RUTHLESS ZONE)

By yourz truly RZE

This video is a music video for the song "Gimme The Loot" by RZE and Manash Ghale, produced by Shigu. The song is from RZE's album "RUTHLESS ZONE." The video features RZE and Manash Ghale performing the song, which has a hip-hop/rap style with lyrics about street life and asserting dominance (0:42-1:02, 1:31-1:53). The phrase "Give me the loot" is a prominent hook throughout the song (1:16-1:28, 2:16-2:20, 3:23-3:34). The video credits Jenish Maharjan as the director, Risheek Pradhan as the creative director, and features visuals by NFTP.

snippet.title: Yabesh Thapa - Shital | OFFICIAL VISUALIZER
snippet.description:
Shital is the second song from the album 'GhaamChhaya' and is a very emotional song for me. It talks about how love would have been different if they had more time. In the end we all turn to dust. Only if he had the power to compel gods to freeze time in place, the story would have a different outcome.

Written, Composed, Produced and Performed by Yabesh Thapa

Recorded at Bazra Creation Records

 ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî• RINGKASAN SIRI ARAFTA (KUMA - Siri Turki)

 Terikat oleh Takdir
 Dua hati. Satu pilihan. Adakah cinta akan menang, atau membalas dendam?

 Berlatarbelakangkan landskap T√ºrkiye yang menawan, *Arafta* menceritakan kisah di mana api kemarahan bertembung dengan panggilan cinta yang senyap. Apabila Ate≈ü, yang menghadapi luka masa lalunya, kembali untuk menyelesaikan akaun, semua keseimbangan berubah. Sementara itu, Mercan cuba melindungi hatinya di dunia ini yang disapu oleh takdir, berjalan di garisan halus antara kepercayaan dan syak wasangka. Rahsia tersembunyi dalam bayang-bayang, kata-kata yang tidak terucap, dan tarikan yang membara‚Ä¶ *Arafta* ialah kisah tentang ketegangan, semangat, dan perhitungan yang semakin meningkat, yang mendorong persoalan "hati atau keangkuhan?" pada setiap selekoh.

 Terikat oleh Takdir
 Dua hati. Satu pilihan. Adakah cinta atau dendam akan menang?

 Berlatarbelakangkan pemandangan Turki yang menakjubkan, Arafta menceritakan kisah di mana api kemarahan bertembung dengan panggilan cinta yang senyap. Di Arafta, dengan setiap langkah, persoalan "hati atau keangkuhan?" Ketegangan nafsu dan perhitungan yang semakin meningkat yang membuat seseorang bertanya soalan itu lagi.

snippet.title: She & Him - I Thought I Saw Your Face Today (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
The official lyric video for "I Thought I Saw Your Face Today" by She & Him from the album 'Volume One' released on Merge Records

Subscribe To She & Him on YouTube: 
https://www.youtube.com/@SheandHimOfficial?sub_confirmation=1

Follow She & Him: 
http://www.sheandhim.com
http://www.instagram.com/sheandhim
http://www.facebook.com/sheandhim
http://www.twitter.com/sheandhim

Stream on Spotify:  https://bit.ly/ITISYFTSpotify
Stream on Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/song/i-thought-i-saw-your-face-today/1839131590
Stream on YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/ITISYFTYTMusic
Buy Vol. 1 on Vinyl: https://sheandhim.shop.redstarmerch.com/product/XZLPSH05/she-him-vol-1

Lyrics: 
I thought I saw your face today
But I just turned my head away
Your face against the trees
But I just see the memories
As they come, as they come

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

I saw it glitter as I grew
And loved it, boy, I never knew
I thought this place was heaven-sent
But now it's just a monument
In my mind, in my mind

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"
The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"

I somehow see what's beautiful
In things that are ephemeral
I'm my only friend of mine
And love is just a piece of time
In the world, in the world

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall...

#SheAndHim #IThoughtISawYourFaceToday

Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 

Jo qudrat ne bikhere the
Bas meri raahon mein
Aur qismat ne sajaaye the
Meri nigaahon mein

Jaane ab kahaan milega 
Kahaan chhupa hoga 
Mil jaata toh rakh leta main
Apni panaahon mein

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Jhaank loon khud mein zara, sab kuch hai andar mere
Lehron pe milta nahin, jo gehre samandar mile 
Mehsoos hoga mujhe, jab khudko pehchanunga
Dil ke andar dekh kar, apni rooh ko jaanunga

Doobega‚Ä¶ Doobega‚Ä¶

Doobega toh tar jaaega
Har zarra mera
Varna tadap ke hi guzrega
Roz marra mera

Kya maine kabhi kiya hai
Thoda ishq bhi khudse 
Mil jaayega phir jo dhoondta hun 
Main darbadar kabse

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai
Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Woh sukoon mujhse hai‚Ä¶
Mujh mein hai sukoon‚Ä¶
